Carl, I got to go
to the bathroom.

01:59:31.494 --> 01:59:32.494
I'm going to be sick.

01:59:32.495 --> 01:59:34.496
Sure.
Let's go in the bathroom.

01:59:41.338 --> 01:59:42.671
Goddamn it!

