Merry Christmas, Frank.

02:04:37.450 --> 02:04:40.285
Hey, I got you
some comic books here.

02:04:46.759 --> 02:04:48.093
How's your daughter?

02:04:48.094 --> 02:04:49.394
What was her name?

02:04:49.395 --> 02:04:50.395
Grace.

02:04:50.396 --> 02:04:51.697
Well... I don't know.

02:04:51.698 --> 02:04:53.899
